These disposable cup filters for Ninja Coffee Maker are made of thinner (disposable coffee bean filter), textured recyclable paper to maintain its shape and better fluidity, will not tear easily.

Moderate thickness-- premium disposable coffee filters for Ninja Coffee Maker trap all the grounds and most of the coffee's natural oils, delivering a smoother, less-bitter flavor. Say goodbye to sediment.

These paper coffee filters are very easy to use, just fill the coffee grounds you need into the disposable filters, after using, just dump the grounds into the trash and no need to wash the reusable coffee pods.
You will receive 200* paper coffee filters that is perfectly compatible with the Ninja coffee machine. If you have any questions, we would be happy to solve them for you.
